Package: MusicFeatClassR
Type: Package
Title: Music Genre Classifier
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Svetlana Koroteeva
Maintainer: Svetlana Koroteeva <svetlana.koroteeva@gmail.com>
Description: 
    This package offers a music genre classifier that combines feature extraction 
    and classification techniques. It automatically categorizes music tracks into 
    genres based on their unique audio characteristics and bibliographic records. 
    The classifier's results can be utilized as a tool for catalogers and for the 
    automatic generation of bibliographical records.
